        {
            "author_association": "NONE",
            "body": "The interesting thing is, that nvim in interactive mode does not take 10 seconds to load on the same SSHFS, it takes less than one second.\nAdditionally, from provided logs, nvim calls these sequence of syscalls around 100 times in a row.\n\nAnd that's why I think that this may be some bug in nvim.",
